::Hot Rod::

"So what do you want to do, Feline?"

::DrillBit::

DrillBit had already been in the CR room, when Phobia's message went
out. He walked up to her and KitKat.
"Whats up?"

::K9::

He got up, and left the CF.
"Beast mode!" In his "dog" mode, he ran off.
